implementation_summary: Added __eq__ and __hash__ methods to Todo class for comparison by id and set operations
acceptance_criteria_met: Todo(id=1, text='a') == Todo(id=1, text='b') returns True
Todo(id=1, text='a') == Todo(id=2, text='a') returns False
hash(Todo(id=1, text='a')) == hash(Todo(id=1, text='b')) returns True
Can use Todo objects in set() and as dict keys
risks: None - minimal change that only affects equality comparison and hashing behavior
